\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ql\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ql\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 They contend for the thesis that central to the effects doctrine in international law is the notion that the effects are harmful. The legislature could not have intended to reach foreign conduct whose effects in SA are benign.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\ql\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057 
