ny other interpretation. However the section contains an important proviso. The interpretations have to be reasonable. Thus even if there is an interpretation consistent with international law that is at variance with another interpretation that is inconsi
stent, we must not prefer the former to the latter unless it is reasonable.}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s1\cf0\qj\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057 
