{\cf1  says our courts have identified two main requirements for the existence of a customary rule: settled practice (usus) and acceptance of an obligation to be bound (opinio juris sive necessitatis).}{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf0\qj\rtlch\af6\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f6\fs20\lang1033\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0{ According to Black\'92s Law Dictionary the opinio juris is \'93}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0{\ltrch\hich\i\loch\i the opinion that an act is necessary by rule of law}{" Black\'92s goes on to state that it is }{\ltrch\hich\i\loch\i \'93 the principle that for a country\'92s conduct to rise to the level of international customary law, it must be 
shown that the conduct stems from the country\'92s belief that international law (rather than moral obligation) mandates the conduct}{.\'94}}}}
{\cf1  According to Dugard our courts now hold the view tha
t universal acceptance is not necessary, general acceptance suffices.}{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf0\qj\rtlch\af6\afs20\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f6\fs20\lang1033\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 Dugard op cit pg. 30.}}}
}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s19\cf3\qj\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057 
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s19\cf0\qj\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ai\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\i\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057\i{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057\i\b0{\cf1 In the }}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057\i\b0{\cf1\ul\ulc0 Asylum}{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf0\qj\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0{\ul\ulc0 Colombia v. Peru, 1950 ICJ Reports 266 at 277}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0 .}}}
{\cf1  case the International Court of Justice held that a practice must constitute, \'93constant and uniform usage\'94 before it will qualify as custom. }}
