the distinction between conduct of an economic nature that took place within the Republic and conduct that took place outside the Republic and which has an \'91effect\'92 within the Republic such as a boycott.}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057\i\b0{\super \chftn{\*\footnote \chftn\pard\plain \ltrpar\s14\cf0\ql\rtlch\ltrch\dbch\hich\loch {\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0{\ul\ulc0\ltrch\hich\f6\fs20\lang1033\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033 Hartford}}{\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033\i0\b0{\ltrch\hich\f6\fs20\lang1033\loch\f6\fs20\lang1033  would be an example of this. The behavior of the British firms amounted to a boycott of United States firms except on certain terms.}}}}
}
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s19\cf1\qj\rtlch\af6\afs24\lang255\ltrch\dbch\af6\langfe255\hich\f4\fs24\lang2057\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057 {\rtlch \ltrch\loch  }
\par \pard\plain \ltrpar\s19\cf0\li720\ri0\lin720\rin0\fi0\ql {\rtlch \ltrch\loch\f4\fs24\lang2057\i0\b0 Recall that earlier in this decision we identified the fact that section 3(1) establishes two bases for jurisdiction \'91economic activity within\'92 and \'91economic activity having an effect within\'92. If harm is to be read into \'91effect\'92 it must also be read into \'91
